"NAME\n"
"\tls - list directory contents.\n"
"SYNOPSIS\n"
"\tls [-h] path\n"
"DESCRIPTION\n"
"\tList information about the FILEs\n"
"\t(the current directory by default).\n"
"OPTIONS\n"
"\tpath -  path of directory.\n"
"\t\tdefaults '/' (root dir).\n"
"\t\tPath format is /dir/filename.\n"
"\t-l - use a long listing format\n"
"SEE ALSO\n"
"\trm\n"
